<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_230_r2l11"><expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> von <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Kere <expan>Tumh<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_230_r2l12">vnd Cuſter / cʒu vvirtʒburg </ab>
<ab type="sender">
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_230_r2l13"><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> / Als Jr mit mir / vnd ich mit ew geredt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_230_r2l14">haben von <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> vnd <expan>Mert<ex>ein</ex></expan> von <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Ker / <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vett<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / vnd <expan>Eb<ex>erhart</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_230_r2l15">von Tünfelt <expan>vveg<ex>en</ex></expan> / als von eins frids / vnd <expan>gütlıche<ex>n</ex></expan> tags </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_230_r2l16"><expan>vveg<ex>en</ex></expan> / das han ich an mein <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> / den Rate cʒü <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> bracht / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_230_r2l17">vnd mit Jn davon geredt / Alſo / <expan>vve<ex>r</ex></expan> es / daʒ Jr mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>vett<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_230_r2l18">auſʒtrügt / daʒ <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> ~ Schürſtab der <expan>gevange<ex>n</ex></expan> iſt / tag het die vveil </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_230_r2l19">der frid vvert / So mainten ſie einen fride <expan>aufcʒeneme<ex>n</ex></expan> auf <expan>pfingſte<ex>n</ex></expan> / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_230_r2l20">vnd <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>gütliche<ex>n</ex></expan> tag . xiiij tag vor pfingſten cʒu <expan>kitʒing<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>cʒeſüche<ex>n</ex></expan> / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_230_r2l21">vnd das der frid angieng auf den Sunntag <expan>Remı<ex>ni</ex>ſce<ex>re</ex></expan> ſchierſt / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_230_r2l22">iſt es / daʒ Jr das alſo auſʒtragt / das lat mich an <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> briefe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_230_r2l23">beÿ diſem poten <expan>vvid<ex>er</ex></expan> vviſʒen / So vvil ich die fridbrief <expan>mache<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_230_r2l24">laſʒen / vnd dohin ſchicken / als ich nehſt von ew geſchieden bin / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_230_r2l25"><expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> Jn <expan>vıg<ex>i</ex>lıa</expan> Mathie <expan>Ap<ex>oſto</ex>lı</expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_230_r2l30">von <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vvÿriche<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Trewhtling<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<div type="cedula"><ab facs="#facs_230_r2l26">Cedula incluſa </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_230_r2l27">VVas <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan> vvillen darÿnne ſeÿ / das laſʒet mich endlich <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> wiſʒen / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_230_r2l28">beÿ diſem boten / vnd ich han auch <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> poten <expan>empfolhe<ex>n</ex></expan> / ob Jr Jn hieſʒet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_230_r2l29">daʒ er <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒwen tag <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dreÿ <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> antvvurt vvarten ſölt / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_230" id="114v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> von <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Kere,
                                <expan>tumh<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> und custer czu Wirczburg <ab type="sender"> </ab>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>, als ir mit mir und
                                                ich mit ew geredt haben von
                                                  <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>Mert<ex>ein</ex></expan> von
                                                  <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Ker,
                                                  <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>vett<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, und
                                                  <expan>Eb<ex>erhart</ex></expan> von Tünfelt
                                                  <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, als von eins frids
                                                und <expan>gütliche<ex>n</ex></expan> tags
                                                  <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, das han ich an mein
                                                  <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, den rate czü
                                                  <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>, bracht und mit
                                                in davon geredt; also <expan>we<ex>r</ex></expan>
                                                es, daz ir mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vett<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ausztrügt, daz
                                                  <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Schürstab, der
                                                  <expan>gevange<ex>n</ex></expan> ist, tag het, die
                                                weil der frid wert, so mainten sie, einen fride
                                          <expan>aufczeneme<ex>n</ex></expan> <app><note><q type="date">auf
                                            <expan>pfingste<ex>n</ex></expan></q>31.05.1411</note></app> und
                                                  <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>gütliche<ex>n</ex></expan> tag <app><note><q type="date">xiiii tag vor
                                            pfingsten</q>17.05.1411</note></app> czu <expan>Kiczing<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>cze süche<ex>n</ex></expan>, und das der frid
                                            angieng <app><note><q type="date">auf den sunntag
                                                  <expan>remi<ex>ni</ex>sce<ex>re</ex></expan>
                                              schierst</q>08.03.1411</note></app>. Und ist es, daz ir das also ausztragt, das
                                                lat mich an <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> briefe bey
                                                disem poten <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> wiszen, so
                                                wil ich die fridbrief <expan>mache<ex>n</ex></expan>
                                                laszen und dohin schicken, als ich nehst von ew
                                                geschieden bin. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in
                                                  <expan>vig<ex>i</ex>lia</expan> Mathie
                                          <expan>ap<ex>osto</ex>li</expan> etc. <lb/>Von
                                                  <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Wyriche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Trewhtling<ex>en</ex></expan>.</ab></div><div type="cedula">
<ab>Cedula inclusa</ab>
<ab> Was <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan> willen darynne sey,
                                                das laszet mich endlich
                                                  <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> wiszen bey disem
                                                boten, und ich han auch <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
                                                poten <expan>empfolhe<ex>n</ex></expan>, ob ir in
                                                hieszet, daz er <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> czwen
                                                tag <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> drey
                                                  <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> antwurt warten
                                                sölt.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
